      "parameters": {
        "content": "# ðŸ§¾ AI Expense Audit & Reimbursement Agent\n\n**Use Case:** Finance & HR Operations\n**The Problem:** Manual expense reporting is a bottleneck. Finance teams waste hours reviewing receipts for policy violations, and employees wait weeks for reimbursement.\n**The Solution:** An autonomous \"Audit Agent\" that visually reads receipts, enforces company policy deterministically, and handles approvals/rejections instantly.\n\n**Architecture:**\n1. **Visual Extraction:** Uses **GPT-4o Vision** to extract Vendor, Date, and Amount from raw imagesâ€”no manual entry required.\n2. **Policy Engine:** Deterministic `If` logic enforces rules (e.g., \"Meals > $100 require review\" or \"Alcohol detected\").\n3. **Feedback Loops:**\n    * **Rejection:** Bad images triggers an instant \"Retake\" email.\n    * **Escalation:** High-risk items trigger a **Slack Alert** with the receipt image attached for manager review.\n    * **Approval:** Safe items trigger an instant \"Approved\" email.\n4. **Audit Trail:** All actions are logged to a central Ledger (Google Sheets).",
        "height": 432,
        "width": 832,
        "color": 3
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -1568,
        -944
