      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "f500fac4-6a05-4101-a566-47230164530b",
      "name": "Sticky Note"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### ðŸ‘ï¸ Multimodal Ingestion Layer\n\n* **Zero-Entry Input:** Employees simply snap a photo. No manual typing required.\n* **Vision & Reasoning:** The AI Agent performs two tasks in one pass:\n    1. **OCR:** Extracts hard data (Amount: $74.79).\n    2. **Analysis:** Scans for risk factors (e.g., detecting \"Miller Lite\" implies Alcohol).",
        "height": 400,
        "width": 528,
        "color": 5
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
