      "id": "c6d69d6d-013c-40db-bc6a-0191dc297c31",
      "name": "Sticky Note1"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### ðŸ›¡ï¸ Validation Gate\n\n* **Sanity Check:** Before processing, the system verifies if the uploaded file is actually a legible receipt.\n* **Closed Loop:** If the image is blurry or invalid, the workflow terminates the main path and immediately emails the user with the specific error reason (e.g., \"Image Unreadable\"), preventing database pollution.",
        "height": 688,
        "width": 278,
        "color": 4
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
