      "name": "Sticky Note2"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### âš–ï¸ Policy Enforcement Engine\n\n* **Deterministic Logic:** Applies hard business rules (e.g., `Amount > $100` OR `Risk Flag == True`).\n* **Branching:**\n    * **Path A (Risk):** Routes to manual review.\n    * **Path B (Safe):** Routes to auto-approval.",
        "height": 736,
        "width": 336,
        "color": 7
      },
