    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### ðŸ”” Human-in-the-Loop & Audit\n\n* **Rich Alerts:** The **Merge Node** re-attaches the original receipt image to the data stream, allowing the **Slack Node** to post the actual image to the manager for immediate context.\n* **Instant Feedback:** Approved users receive an HTML email confirmation immediately.\n* **Ledger:** Final state (Approved/Review) is logged to the database for month-end reconciliation.",
